data.title: Buy Tickets Now - The Tatler Bystander Ball
data.meta_description: Get them tickets for THE teen party of the summer. Tatler has teamed up with Johnnie B to host its first ever ticketed event, the  TATLER BYSTANDER BALL.
data.text:
Have a teen in your life? Send them this link post-haste! Our sister magazine, Tatler, has teamed up with Johnnie B to host its first ever ticketed event, the TATLER BYSTANDER BALL.

Tatler are inviting 500 teenagers aged 13-16 to join them on TUESDAY 9 JULY at Supperclub, Notting Hill, for what promises to be THE party of the summer.

The ball is from 7:30pm to 12:30am and includes:

FREE mocktails and canapés

FREE instant photo booth

Celebrity appearances and entertainment

Live circus acts

Live DJ

Video DJ

FREE goodie bag filled with Tatler and Johnnie B delights

…and much more.

The dress code is 'black tie on the beach', so tell them to team their sparkles with surf shorts, dress shirt with flip-flops, full-length skirt with full-on florals... or whatever takes their fancy!

Follow the Tatler Bystander Ball on Facebook and @BystanderBall on Twitter to be the first to hear about exciting announcements, have your say on the playlist and see party photos.
